channel.title: Making a new playerRights level ~ DeltaScape Base
channel.description:
Alright, so I was wondering.
Does anyone know how to make a COMPLETELY new playerRights level on DeltaScape Base?
Like, theres playerRights 1, 2, 3, 4 (Mod, Admin, Owner, Hidden).
So I was wondering if it was possible to make a playerRights level of 5?
1 - Mod. 2 - Admin. 3 - Co Owner. 4 - Hidden. 5 - Owner.
If this is possible please, if you could direct me to a TuT or show me how to, I'd be willing to rep++ for the help.
Sincerely, Clayton.
